{"tid":1566821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想變雨革2.0再慘輸 唱夠歌就唔該做認真野","createTime":"2019-09-13T18:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:12:13.000Z","uid":144833,"like":42,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"d0df1d38b18916f94e6595e9cebf49ec1417b8b7","tid":1566821,"uid":144833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:24:57.000Z","msg":"唔係完全唔比唱 但唱足成個禮拜 <br />\n日日唱 仲要加埋樂器 又彈又唱<br />\n係時候停喇 <br />\n推返新屋嶺 集中返五大訴求 同啲活動post好唔好<br />\n白宮聯署啲po推極都推唔起<br />\n唔好再返返雨革果時咁 覺得唱歌=抗爭啦<br />\n<br />\n我知咁講一定比人屌<br />\n但首歌真係好難聽 歌詞又橋口 <br />\n真係唔認同感人/激昂<br />\n成陣濃濃嘅左膠味 <br />\n同其他社運左膠歌到底有咩分別<br />\n但你地鍾意唱<br />\n我地都唯有少數服從多數由你唱<br />\n<br />\n咁唱咗成個禮拜 咩都夠啦<br />\n諗住你地會停<br />\n點知繼續唱 一個二個仲要拎埋樂譜彈<br />\n<br />\n美國議會唔係事必會通過人權法案架<br />\n新屋嶺嘅手足連中秋都過唔到<br />\n就黎提堂被控暴動嘅手足又少人理<br />\n真係想贏嘅話<br />\n依家鬆完 就好認真返 做認真野去抗爭喇<br />\n<br />\n認真野如下：<br />\n德國戰線WELT投票：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1566331/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1566331/page/1</a><br />\n德國戰線DW留言：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1561785/page/1?post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1561785/page/1?post=1</a><br />\nG20十一眾籌：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1564990/page/1?post=2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1564990/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n醫管局文件：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563148/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563148/page/1</a><br />\n所有白宮聯署唔該簽齊：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1566515/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1566515/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n活動文宣圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnLQ8ps.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnLQ8ps.jpg&h=0e88afb8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Uhv8pt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Uhv8pt.jpg&h=ec96894d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gVZne4u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgVZne4u.jpg&h=618cb7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WxNoJXQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxNoJXQ.png&h=49f2f33d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"706c274b8555c3d9b82575487c1532ad9b00a731","tid":1566821,"uid":263699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:26:17.000Z","msg":"推 915 維園見！"},{"pid":"0743f2d83a74825aade172fc9a6277b4c4a4fbc9","tid":1566821,"uid":300514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puGAz6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpuGAz6p.jpg&h=5b276dc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d114d6801cba02f7e84cf86424bc3db068f29d8","tid":1566821,"uid":300514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0743f2d83a74825aade172fc9a6277b4c4a4fbc9","tid":1566821,"uid":300514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puGAz6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpuGAz6p.jpg&h=5b276dc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adcHe7i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadcHe7i.jpg&h=0b5bf5a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58e7d26f1907c3bcc01b37aa8579db70a8474630","tid":1566821,"uid":311837,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:40:45.000Z","msg":"無人話過星期一至五唱歌，星期六日就唔出去。放工班西裝友一係去 IFC 唱歌，一係返歸，邊樣好？定係叫和理非去圍狗屋先叫好？"},{"pid":"8805de10a1ba048631f54eaecc1c8f3bedc8e1aa","tid":1566821,"uid":144833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:42:54.000Z","msg":"仲有唔該將唱歌嘅時間用少少去多謝返國際戰線<br />\n台灣人為咗我地拍片仲出埋黎遊行<br />\n片：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2253137151438559?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2253137151438559%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=8ad0723e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2253137151438559?sfns=mo</a><br />\n韓國人寫歌又拍片<br />\n歌：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GRqSSRBuVfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGRqSSRBuVfQ&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=2ac756ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GRqSSRBuVfQ</a><br />\n片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Kor6mu01lGY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKor6mu01lGY&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=ef9a7567\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Kor6mu01lGY</a><br />\n圖：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B2JgR5dBlx8/?igshid=1jyzbuqriofhy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB2JgR5dBlx8%2F%3Figshid%3D1jyzbuqriofhy&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=2d6cdf37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB2JgR5dBlx8%2F%3Figshid%3D1jyzbuqriofhy&h=8b995ea6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B2JgR5dBlx8/?igshid=1jyzbuqriofhy</a><br />\n波蘭人又拍片<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y3iFiSiJYX4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy3iFiSiJYX4&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=a39d432f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y3iFiSiJYX4</a><br />\n德國人直頭比我地嘅手足做難民<br />\n仲有好多其他不能盡數<br />\n唔該見到就留返個言多謝返佢地 長期作戰 聚人心唔係一下就夠<br />\n韓文：지지해주셔서 감사합니다. 5대요구, 하나도 빠져선 안된다.<br />\n1. 송환법 완전히 철폐<br />\n2. 폭동 규정 철회<br />\n3. 체포된 시위자 공소철회 및 무죄석방<br />\n4. 공권력 남용 강경 진압에 나선 경찰 문책<br />\n5. 행정명령으로 국회를 해산시켜 즉각 행정장관과 입법회 보통 선거 도입<br />\n德文: Herzlichen Dank f&uuml;r all Ihre Unterst&uuml;tzung. F&uuml;nf Hauptforderungen, niemand weniger! <br />\n1. Allgemeines Wahlrecht f&uuml;r den Regierungschef und auch Legislativrat. <br />\n2. Die Freilassung von festgenommenen Demonstranten. <br />\n3. Die Einrichtung eines unabh&auml;ngigen Untersuchungsausschusses. <br />\n4. Die R&uuml;cknahme der Deklarierung der Proteste als Aufruhr. <br />\n5. Die komplette R&uuml;cknahme des Auslieferungsgesetzes.<br />\n<br />\n中英：&ldquo;Five Core Demands, All or None.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\nFormally Withdrawal (without any ambiguity) of the Extradition Bill<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\nWithdrawal of the characterization of the all related conflicts as &ldquo;riot&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\nDismiss all charges made against demonstrators who protested against the Bill;<br />\nGuarantee no further charges will be made.<br />\n<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\nAccountability for Police Abuse of Authority and Excessive Force<br />\n(Set up an independent commission of inquiry to conduct impartial investigation).<br />\n<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\nDissolve the Legislative Council with an executive order;<br />\nImmediately implement Genuine Universal Suffrage <br />\n(direct election both the Chief Executive and the Legislative Council)."},{"pid":"d4295f23127eba0c734f88ad742cb9587b3324b9","tid":1566821,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:43:03.000Z","msg":"【終極核彈】《願榮光》之後－成立海外臨時民主政府<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566796</a><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光》之後。。。<br />\n天滅中共 平反六四！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海外臨時政府 自由香港<br />\nFREE HONG KONG</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/freehongkonghkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehongkonghkg&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=d23368c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/freehongkonghkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMTNBB.jpg&h=16392072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓這攬炒旗隨風飄揚！（logo已獲攬炒巴授權使用）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人哋北韓都做到 香港唔係做唔到呀嘛？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"b1ba5984d7fd8021979683d4bd18e782da76f7bb","tid":1566821,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T20:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df4c59cd2247bad356036fafc9a8d33d259baa8","tid":1566821,"uid":25468,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T20:54:42.000Z","msg":"雨革失敗係因為互相割蓆，唔撚關唱歌事"},{"pid":"2a9ca868583419e851848cc33b254bbc13ff5d43","tid":1566821,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3df4c59cd2247bad356036fafc9a8d33d259baa8","tid":1566821,"uid":25468,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T20:54:42.000Z","msg":"雨革失敗係因為互相割蓆，唔撚關唱歌事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T21:02:35.000Z","msg":"再搞嘉年華就真係唔慌無人割"},{"pid":"7c661a7ed8f83c642f47d5b12432ebab49b5c097","tid":1566821,"uid":60935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58e7d26f1907c3bcc01b37aa8579db70a8474630","tid":1566821,"uid":311837,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:40:45.000Z","msg":"無人話過星期一至五唱歌，星期六日就唔出去。放工班西裝友一係去 IFC 唱歌，一係返歸，邊樣好？定係叫和理非去圍狗屋先叫好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20