rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T02:37:15.000Z","msg":"你見我講得咁客氣都比人屌就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無話唔比和理非唱歌 你唱一兩日咪算<br />\n但唱到行動post又唔推 活動又唔文宣就唔得啦<br />\n915 民陣大遊行要出啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a16be4c0bfd898f14baf2ae8cbf708da7c277a","tid":1566821,"uid":70120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"聽日見！借個位post埋 fb見到 好緊要 <br />\n<br />\n【你敢說：天滅中共嗎？】<br />\n<br />\n唔知你哋知唔知，而家形勢好不妙，我哋對美國嘅求助完全唔夠力。對付中共只有兩個方向，一係，拉攏美國企香港人嗰邊，一係，谷撚到佢支爆。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">拉攏美國企香港人呢邊</span></span>，我哋用咗幾多力？在戰場上出美國旗隊，唱美國歌，戰場下推白宮聯署，Twitter攻勢，但<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢條戰線已就快<span style=\"color: red;\">潰不成軍</span></span></ins>。<br />\n<br />\n喺諗到方法前，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">簽爆呢個聯署，係大家嘅責任</span></span></strong>。有人扮抗爭但想暗幫中共，我哋係想中國支爆呀。<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n簽＞等電郵＞確認簽署＞叫十個朋友簽<br />\n<br />\n🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《未夠數》</span></span>🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n==========<br />\n如香港政府實施緊急法，請美國廢除《香港政策法》<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-abolish-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act-if-hong-kong-implement-emergency-regulations-ordinance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-abolish-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act-if-hong-kong-implement-emergency-regulations-ordinance&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=499d678a\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-abolish-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act-if-hong-kong-implement-emergency-regulations-ordinance</a><br />\n//<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民 (Deadline Oct 11)<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=70d45459\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force</a><br />\n//<br />\n請美國政府向中華人民共和國追討清朝國債 (Deadline Oct 4)<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=8ad16d6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n//<br />\n請通過《香港人權及民主法案》，追究香港警察性暴力 (Deadline Sep 28)<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/stop-hk-police-sexually-assaulting-protestors-please-pass-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fstop-hk-police-sexually-assaulting-protestors-please-pass-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=107019de\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/stop-hk-police-sexually-assaulting-protestors-please-pass-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a><br />\n//<br />\n拯救國泰航空，保障經濟自由 (Deadline Sep 21)<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-rescue-cathay-pacific-airways-please-support-hong-kongs-fight-defending-economic-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-rescue-cathay-pacific-airways-please-support-h