言多謝返佢地 長期作戰 聚人心唔係一下就夠<br />\n韓文：지지해주셔서 감사합니다. 5대요구, 하나도 빠져선 안된다.<br />\n1. 송환법 완전히 철폐<br />\n2. 폭동 규정 철회<br />\n3. 체포된 시위자 공소철회 및 무죄석방<br />\n4. 공권력 남용 강경 진압에 나선 경찰 문책<br />\n5. 행정명령으로 국회를 해산시켜 즉각 행정장관과 입법회 보통 선거 도입<br />\n德文: Herzlichen Dank f&uuml;r all Ihre Unterst&uuml;tzung. F&uuml;nf Hauptforderungen, niemand weniger! <br />\n1. Allgemeines Wahlrecht f&uuml;r den Regierungschef und auch Legislativrat. <br />\n2. Die Freilassung von festgenommenen Demonstranten. <br />\n3. Die Einrichtung eines unabh&auml;ngigen Untersuchungsausschusses. <br />\n4. Die R&uuml;cknahme der Deklarierung der Proteste als Aufruhr. <br />\n5. Die komplette R&uuml;cknahme des Auslieferungsgesetzes.<br />\n<br />\n中英：&ldquo;Five Core Demands, All or None.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\nFormally Withdrawal (without any ambiguity) of the Extradition Bill<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\nWithdrawal of the characterization of the all related conflicts as &ldquo;riot&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\nDismiss all charges made against demonstrators who protested against the Bill;<br />\nGuarantee no further charges will be made.<br />\n<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\nAccountability for Police Abuse of Authority and Excessive Force<br />\n(Set up an independent commission of inquiry to conduct impartial investigation).<br />\n<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\nDissolve the Legislative Council with an executive order;<br />\nImmediately implement Genuine Universal Suffrage <br />\n(direct election both the Chief Executive and the Legislative Council)."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T02:41:51.000Z","msg":"呢個好！！"},{"pid":"2a13519ff93bc57f2743c792a78111a94d9ee047","tid":1566821,"uid":144833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67a16be4c0bfd898f14baf2ae8cbf708da7c277a","tid":1566821,"uid":70120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"聽日見！借個位post埋 fb見到 好緊要 <br />\n<br />\n【你敢說：天滅中共嗎？】<br />\n<br />\n唔知你哋知唔知，而家形勢好不妙，我哋對美國嘅求助完全唔夠力。對付中共只有兩個方向，一係，拉攏美國企香港人嗰邊，一係，谷撚到佢支爆。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">拉攏美國企香港人呢邊</span></span>，我哋用咗幾多力？在戰場上出美國旗隊，唱美國歌，戰場下推白宮聯署，Twitter攻勢，但<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢條戰線已就快<span style=\"color: red;\">潰不成軍</span></span></ins>。<br />\n<br />\n喺諗到方法前，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">簽爆呢個聯署，係大家嘅責任</span></span></strong>。有人扮抗爭但想暗幫中共，我哋係想中國支爆呀。<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n簽＞等電郵＞確認簽署＞叫十個朋友簽<br />\n<br />\n🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《未夠數》</span></span>🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n==========<br />\n如香港政府實施緊急法，請美國廢除《香港政策法》<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-abolish-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act-if-hong-kong-implement-emergency-regulations-ordinance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-abolish-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act-if-hong-kong-implement-emergency-regulations-ordinance&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=499d678a\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-abolish-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act-if-hong-kong-implement-emergency-regulations-ordinance</a><br />\n//<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民 (Deadline Oct 11)<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=70d45459\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force</a><br />\n//<br />\n請美國政府向中華人民共和國追討清朝國債 (Deadline Oct 4)<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/r